---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="How We Work | Berrystock Solutions">
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>How We Work</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        We design and deliver structured cloud platforms and integrated business systems 
        with security, clarity and long-term operability built in from day one.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Our Approach</h2>

      <div class="grid">

        <div class="card">
          <h3>Outcome-Led Architecture</h3>
          <p>
            We begin with business objectives, not tooling. Architecture decisions 
            are aligned to risk tolerance, growth plans, and operational maturity.
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Clear platform structure</li>
            <li>Defined ownership & access models</li>
            <li>Scalable foundations</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3>Secure by Design</h3>
          <p>
            Identity-first access patterns and restricted management surfaces 
            reduce risk without increasing operational friction.
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>MFA & conditional access alignment</li>
            <li>Least-privilege access control</li>
            <li>Hardened management endpoints</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3>Structured Delivery</h3>
          <p>
            Change is delivered with staged rollout, rollback planning, and 
            documented operating procedures.
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Cutover & rollback strategy</li>
            <li>Pre-flight validation</li>
            <li>Runbooks & handover-ready documentation</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3>Business Systems Integration</h3>
          <p>
            We connect cloud infrastructure with ERP, CRM, telephony, and workflow 
            automation to remove manual effort and improve visibility.
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>System-to-system integration</li>
            <li>Email & identity alignment</li>
            <li>Structured data flows</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3>Operational Discipline</h3>
          <p>
            Platforms are designed to be maintainable. Visibility, monitoring, 
            cost control, and change governance are embedded.
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Monitoring & alerting structure</li>
            <li>Cost optimisation controls</li>
            <li>Clear change management approach</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3>Automation-Driven Engineering</h3>
          <p>
            Repeatable patterns reduce risk and accelerate delivery while ensuring 
            environments remain consistent over time.
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Infrastructure as Code</li>
            <li>Deployment standardisation</li>
            <li>Operational scripting</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

      </div>

      <div style="margin-top:30px;">
        <a class="cta" href="/contact">Start a Conversation</a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
